    <title>LaTex公式入门</title>
    <link href="https://blog.ibeihai.ml/2023/04/24/LaTex%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/"/>
    <id>https://blog.ibeihai.ml/2023/04/24/LaTex%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/</id>
    <published>2023-04-24T13:54:23.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-04-24T14:08:49.648Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><ol><li>各种运算符和命令产生的格式效果都只对其后面大括号内的各字符有效（若其中只有一个字符则可以省略大括号）。</li><li>英文字母只有在表示<strong>变量</strong>（或单一字符的<strong>函数名称</strong>，如$f(x)$）时才使用斜体，其余情况都应使用罗马体（直立体），表示方法见<a href="#2.%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E6%A0%87">这部分</a>。</li></ol></blockquote><h1 id="1-希腊字母"><a href="#1-希腊字母" class="headerlink" title="1.希腊字母"></a>1.希腊字母</h1><p>一些示例：</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\delta</span>,<span class="keyword">\lambda</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\Delta</span>,<span class="keyword">\Lambda</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\Alpha</span>,<span class="keyword">\Beta</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\phi</span>,<span class="keyword">\varphi</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\epsilon</span>,<span class="keyword">\varepsilon</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\delta,\lambda\<br>\Delta,\Lambda\<br>\Alpha,\Beta\<br>\phi,\varphi\<br>\epsilon,\varepsilon<br>$$</p><p>其中的一些字母存在变体，如第4、5行的两个字符，使用的是\ <strong>var</strong>phi 和 \ <strong>var</strong>pesion (&#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>var</strong>iant，变体&#x3D;&#x3D;)</p><p>希腊字符-latex代码对照表：</p><p><img src="https://imgs.beihai.one/i/image-20230420184518911.webp" alt="image-20230420184518911" loading="lazy"></p><h1 id="2-上下标"><a href="#2-上下标" class="headerlink" title="2.上下标"></a>2.上下标</h1><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a<span class="built_in">^</span>2,a<span class="built_in">_</span>1<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">x<span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;y+z&#125;,p<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;ij&#125;<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>a^2,a_1\<br>x^{y+z},p_{ij}\<br>$$</p><p>默认为斜体，非变量使用直立体，两种方法，其中 &#x3D;&#x3D;\rm(<strong>r</strong>o<strong>m</strong>an，罗马体)&#x3D;&#x3D;：</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x<span class="built_in">_</span>i,x<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\rm</span> i&#125;,x<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\text</span> i&#125;<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>x_i,x_{\rm i},x_{\text i}\<br>$$</p><p>\text 可以显示空格， \rm 不显示空格，如下：</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\text</span>&#123;A B&#125;,<span class="keyword">\rm</span>&#123;A B&#125;<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\text</span> A B,<span class="keyword">\rm</span> A B<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\text</span>&#123;e&#125;,<span class="keyword">\text</span>&#123;i&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\begin{align}<br>\text{A B},\rm{A B} \<br>\text A B,\rm A B\<br>\text{e},\text{i}<br>\end{align}<br>$$</p><p>自然对数 $\text{e}$ ，虚数单位 $\text{i}$ ，也使用直立体。</p><h1 id="3-分式与根式"><a href="#3-分式与根式" class="headerlink" title="3.分式与根式"></a>3.分式与根式</h1><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>frac</strong>（<strong>frac</strong>tion，分数）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>dfrac</strong>（<strong>d</strong>isplay-style）分数线<strong>自适应</strong>大小&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;1&#125;&#123;2&#125;,<span class="keyword">\frac</span> 1  2,<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\frac</span> 1 &#123;x+y&#125;<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\frac</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\dfrac</span> 1 x + 1&#125;&#123;y + 1&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\frac{1}{2},\frac 1 2,\<br>\frac 1 {x+y}\<br>\frac {\dfrac 1 x + 1}{y + 1}<br>$$</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>sqrt</strong>（<strong>sq</strong>uare <strong>r</strong>oo<strong>t</strong>，平方根）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\sqrt</span> 2,<span class="keyword">\sqrt</span>&#123;x+y&#125;,<span class="keyword">\sqrt</span>[3]x</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\sqrt 2,\sqrt{x+y},\sqrt[3]x<br>$$</p><h1 id="4-普通运算符"><a href="#4-普通运算符" class="headerlink" title="4.普通运算符"></a>4.普通运算符</h1><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>c</strong>dot（<strong>c</strong>entre，中心）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>div</strong>（<strong>div</strong>ide，除）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>pm</strong>（<strong>p</strong>lus-<strong>m</strong>inus，正负）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>mp</strong>（<strong>m</strong>inus-<strong>p</strong>lus，负正）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>ge</strong>（<strong>g</strong>reater than or <strong>e</strong>uqal，大于等于）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>le</strong>（<strong>l</strong>ess than or <strong>e</strong>uqal，小于等于）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>ne</strong>（<strong>n</strong>ot <strong>e</strong>uqal，不等于）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>approx</strong>（<strong>approx</strong>imate，约等于）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>equiv</strong>（<strong>equiv</strong>alent，恒等于）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\math<strong>bb</strong>（<strong>b</strong>lackboard <strong>b</strong>old，黑粗体，可用来表示数集符号，部分字母有效）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\math<strong>cal</strong>（<strong>cal</strong>ligraphy，书法，如傅里叶变换符号，见下文）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\math<strong>scr</strong>（<strong>scr</strong>ipt，手迹）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">+-<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\times</span>,<span class="keyword">\cdot</span>,<span class="keyword">\div</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\pm</span>,<span class="keyword">\mp</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&lt;,<span class="keyword">\ge</span>,<span class="keyword">\le</span>,<span class="keyword">\gg</span>,<span class="keyword">\ll</span>,<span class="keyword">\ne</span>,<span class="keyword">\approx</span>,<span class="keyword">\equiv</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\cap</span>,<span class="keyword">\cup</span>,<span class="keyword">\in</span>,<span class="keyword">\notin</span>,<span class="keyword">\subseteq</span>,<span class="keyword">\subsetneqq</span>,<span class="keyword">\varnothing</span>,<span class="keyword">\complement</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\because</span>,<span class="keyword">\therefore</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\mathbb</span> R,<span class="keyword">\R</span>,<span class="keyword">\Q</span>,<span class="keyword">\N</span>,<span class="keyword">\Z</span><span class="built_in">_</span>+<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\mathcal</span> F,<span class="keyword">\mathscr</span> F</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>+-\<br>\times,\cdot,\div\<br>\pm,\mp\</p><blockquote><p>&lt;,\ge,\le,\gg,\ll,\ne,\approx,\equiv\<br>\cap,\cup,\in,\notin,\subseteq,\subsetneqq,\varnothing,\complement\<br>\because,\therefore\<br>\mathbb R\<br>\mathcal F,\mathscr F<br>$$</p></blockquote><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>v</strong>dots（<strong>v</strong>ertical，垂直的）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>d</strong>dots（<strong>d</strong>iagonal，对角的）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\cdots</span>,<span class="keyword">\vdots</span>,<span class="keyword">\ddots</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\cdots,\vdots,\ddots<br>$$</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>infty</strong>（<strong>inf</strong>ini<strong>ty</strong>，无穷）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>partial</strong>（<strong>partial</strong>，偏微分）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\<strong>prop</strong>to（<strong>prop</strong>ortional <strong>to</strong>，正比于）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>circ</strong>（<strong>circ</strong>le，圆形，使用^符号将圆形置于右上角表示度）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\infty</span>,<span class="keyword">\partial</span>,<span class="keyword">\nabla</span>,<span class="keyword">\propto</span>,<span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\circ</span>&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\infty,\partial,\nabla,\propto,^{\circ}<br>$$</p><p>运算符号用直体（默认），使用极限符号 \lim 时，如果 $x→0$ 在极限符号右下角，而不在正下方，可在 \lim 后面加 \limits 可强制将 $x→0$ 移到极限符号正下方</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\sin</span> x,<span class="keyword">\sec</span> x,<span class="keyword">\cosh</span> x<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\log</span><span class="built_in">_</span>2 x,<span class="keyword">\ln</span> x,<span class="keyword">\lg</span> x<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\lim</span><span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;x <span class="keyword">\to</span> 0&#125; <span class="keyword">\frac</span> &#123;x&#125; &#123;<span class="keyword">\sin</span> x&#125;<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\lim</span><span class="keyword">\limits</span><span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;x <span class="keyword">\to</span> 0&#125; <span class="keyword">\frac</span> &#123;x&#125; &#123;<span class="keyword">\sin</span> x&#125;<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\max</span> x</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\sin x,\sec x,\cosh x\<br>\log_2 x,\ln x,\lg x\<br>\lim_{x \to 0} \frac {x} {\sin x}\<br>\lim\limits_{x \to 0} \frac {x} {\sin x}\<br>\max x<br>$$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\text</span>&#123;MSE&#125;(x)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\text{MSE}(x)<br>$$</p><h1 id="5-大型运算符"><a href="#5-大型运算符" class="headerlink" title="5.大型运算符"></a>5.大型运算符</h1><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>prod</strong>（<strong>prod</strong>uct，乘积）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\sum</span>,<span class="keyword">\prod</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\sum</span><span class="built_in">_</span>i,<span class="keyword">\sum</span><span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;i=0&#125;<span class="built_in">^</span>n<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\sum</span><span class="keyword">\limits</span><span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;i=1&#125;<span class="built_in">^</span>n x<span class="built_in">_</span>i&#125;&#123;<span class="keyword">\prod</span><span class="keyword">\limits</span><span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;i=1&#125;<span class="built_in">^</span>n x<span class="built_in">_</span>i&#125;<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\sum,\prod\<br>\sum_i,\sum_{i&#x3D;0}^n\<br>\frac{\sum\limits_{i&#x3D;1}^n x_i}{\prod\limits_{i&#x3D;1}^n x_i}\<br>$$</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>int</strong>（<strong>int</strong>egral，积分）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\int</span>,<span class="keyword">\iint</span>,<span class="keyword">\iiint</span>,<span class="keyword">\oint</span>,<span class="keyword">\oiint</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\int</span><span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;-<span class="keyword">\infty</span>&#125;<span class="built_in">^</span>0 f(x)<span class="keyword">\,</span><span class="keyword">\text</span>&#123;d&#125;x</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\int,\iint,\iiint,\oint,\oiint\<br>\int_{-\infty}^0 f(x),\text{d}x<br>$$</p><p>上式的积分中用到了 \text 将 d 改为直立体，使用 , 在被积函数和 d 之间加入了一个小间隔。以下是各种不同的间隔：</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a<span class="keyword">\,</span> a<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">a<span class="keyword">\ </span>a<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">a<span class="keyword">\quad</span> a<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">a<span class="keyword">\qquad</span> a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>a, a\<br>a\ a\<br>a\quad a\<br>a\qquad a<br>$$</p><h1 id="6-标注符号"><a href="#6-标注符号" class="headerlink" title="6.标注符号"></a>6.标注符号</h1><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>vec</strong>（<strong>vec</strong>tor，向量）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\vec</span> x, <span class="keyword">\overrightarrow</span> &#123;AB&#125;<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\bar</span> x, <span class="keyword">\overline</span>&#123;AB&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\vec x, \overrightarrow {AB}\<br>\bar x, \overline{AB}<br>$$</p><p>其他标注符号</p><p><img src="https://imgs.beihai.one/i/image-20230420192934179.webp" alt="image-20230420192934179" loading="lazy"></p><h1 id="7-箭头"><a href="#7-箭头" class="headerlink" title="7.箭头"></a>7.箭头</h1><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\leftarrow</span>,<span class="keyword">\Rightarrow</span>,<span class="keyword">\Leftrightarrow</span>,<span class="keyword">\longleftarrow</span>,<span class="keyword">\longleftrightarrow</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\leftarrow,\Rightarrow,\Leftrightarrow,\longleftarrow,\longleftrightarrow<br>$$</p><p>其他箭头</p><p><img src="https://imgs.beihai.one/i/image-20230420193112959.webp" alt="image-20230420193112959" loading="lazy"></p><h1 id="8-括号与界定符"><a href="#8-括号与界定符" class="headerlink" title="8.括号与界定符"></a>8.括号与界定符</h1><p>常见的括号、向上取整、向下取整和绝对值：</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\l<strong>ceil</strong>（<strong>ceil</strong>，英文中是天花板的意思，有向上的意思）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\r<strong>floor</strong>（<strong>floor</strong>，地板，与天花板对应）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">([])<span class="keyword">\&#123;</span><span class="keyword">\&#125;</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\lceil</span>,<span class="keyword">\rceil</span>,<span class="keyword">\lfloor</span>,<span class="keyword">\rfloor</span>,||<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>([]){}\<br>\lceil,\rceil,\lfloor,\rfloor,||\<br>$$</p><p>括号前使用 \left 和 \right 命令，使括号大小可以&#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>自适应</strong>&#x3D;&#x3D;：</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\left</span>(0,<span class="keyword">\frac</span> 1 a <span class="keyword">\right</span>]<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\left(0,\frac 1 a \right]\<br>$$</p><p>这里使用 \left. 构建一个虚拟的左括号，与竖线匹配，使得我们可以使用 \right 命令让 | 大小&#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>自适应</strong>&#x3D;&#x3D;：</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\left</span>.<span class="keyword">\frac</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> f&#125;&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> x&#125;<span class="keyword">\right</span>|<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;x=0&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\left.\frac {\partial f}{\partial x}\right|_{x&#x3D;0}<br>$$</p><h1 id="9-多行公式"><a href="#9-多行公式" class="headerlink" title="9.多行公式"></a>9.多行公式</h1><p>构建多行公式环境，默认是对齐：</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;align&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a=b+c+d<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">=e+f</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;align&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\begin{align}</p><p>a&#x3D;b+c+d\<br>&#x3D;e+f</p><p>\end{align}<br>$$</p><p>如需等号处对齐使用 <code>&amp;</code> 符号，该符号英文是 <em>ampersand</em> ：</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;align&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a<span class="built_in">&amp;</span>=b+c+d<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">&amp;</span>=e+f</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;align&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\begin{align}</p><p>a&amp;&#x3D;b+c+d\<br>&amp;&#x3D;e+f</p><p>\end{align}<br>$$</p><h1 id="10-大括号"><a href="#10-大括号" class="headerlink" title="10.大括号"></a>10.大括号</h1><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">f(x)=</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;cases&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\sin</span> x, <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> - <span class="keyword">\pi</span><span class="keyword">\le</span> x <span class="keyword">\le</span> <span class="keyword">\pi</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">0, <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\text</span>&#123;其他&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;cases&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>f(x)&#x3D;<br>\begin{cases}</p><p>\sin x, &amp; - \pi\le x \le \pi\<br>0, &amp; \text{其他}</p><p>\end{cases}<br>$$</p><p>在上方例子中使用了 &#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>换行</strong>&#x3D;&#x3D; 和 &#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>对齐&amp;</strong>&#x3D;&#x3D; 操作。</p><h1 id="11-矩阵"><a href="#11-矩阵" class="headerlink" title="11.矩阵"></a>11.矩阵</h1><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\begin{matrix}（matrix，矩阵）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;matrix&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> b <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\cdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> c <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\vdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\vdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\ddots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\vdots</span> <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">e <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> f <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\cdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;matrix&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\begin{matrix}</p><p>a &amp; b &amp; \cdots &amp; c \<br>\vdots &amp; \vdots &amp; \ddots &amp; \vdots \<br>e &amp; f &amp; \cdots &amp; g</p><p>\end{matrix}<br>$$</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\begin{<strong>b</strong>matrix}（<strong>b</strong>racket，方括号）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;bmatrix&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> b <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\cdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> c <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\vdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\vdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\ddots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\vdots</span> <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">e <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> f <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\cdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;bmatrix&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\begin{bmatrix}</p><p>a &amp; b &amp; \cdots &amp; c \<br>\vdots &amp; \vdots &amp; \ddots &amp; \vdots \<br>e &amp; f &amp; \cdots &amp; g</p><p>\end{bmatrix}<br>$$</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\begin{<strong>p</strong>matrix}（<strong>p</strong>arenthesis，圆括号）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;pmatrix&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> b <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\cdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> c <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\vdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\vdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\ddots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\vdots</span> <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">e <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> f <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\cdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;pmatrix&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\begin{pmatrix}</p><p>a &amp; b &amp; \cdots &amp; c \<br>\vdots &amp; \vdots &amp; \ddots &amp; \vdots \<br>e &amp; f &amp; \cdots &amp; g</p><p>\end{pmatrix}<br>$$</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;\begin{<strong>v</strong>matrix}（<strong>v</strong>ertical bar，竖向短线）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;vmatrix&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> b <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\cdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> c <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\vdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\vdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\ddots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\vdots</span> <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">e <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> f <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\cdots</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;vmatrix&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\begin{vmatrix}</p><p>a &amp; b &amp; \cdots &amp; c \<br>\vdots &amp; \vdots &amp; \ddots &amp; \vdots \<br>e &amp; f &amp; \cdots &amp; g<br>\end{vmatrix}<br>$$</p><p>矩阵代号及转置符号用罗马体黑体表示：</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;<strong>bf</strong>（<strong>b</strong>old <strong>f</strong>ace，粗体）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\bf</span> A,<span class="keyword">\bf</span> B<span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\rm</span> T&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\bf A,\bf B^{\rm T}<br>$$</p><h1 id="12-实战演练"><a href="#12-实战演练" class="headerlink" title="12.实战演练"></a>12.实战演练</h1><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">f(x) = <span class="keyword">\frac</span> &#123;1&#125;&#123;<span class="keyword">\sqrt</span>&#123;2<span class="keyword">\pi</span>&#125;<span class="keyword">\sigma</span>&#125;<span class="keyword">\rm</span> e<span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;-<span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;(x-<span class="keyword">\mu</span>)<span class="built_in">^</span>2&#125;&#123;2<span class="keyword">\sigma</span><span class="built_in">^</span>2&#125; &#125; <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">f(x) = <span class="keyword">\frac</span> &#123;1&#125;&#123;<span class="keyword">\sqrt</span>&#123;2<span class="keyword">\pi</span>&#125;<span class="keyword">\sigma</span>&#125; <span class="keyword">\exp</span> <span class="keyword">\left</span>[-<span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;(x-<span class="keyword">\mu</span>)<span class="built_in">^</span>2&#125;&#123;2<span class="keyword">\sigma</span><span class="built_in">^</span>2&#125;<span class="keyword">\right</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>f(x) &#x3D; \frac {1}{\sqrt{2\pi}\sigma}\rm e^{-\frac{(x-\mu)^2}{2\sigma^2} } \<br>f(x) &#x3D; \frac {1}{\sqrt{2\pi}\sigma} \exp \left[-\frac{(x-\mu)^2}{2\sigma^2}\right]<br>$$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\lim</span> <span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;N<span class="keyword">\to</span> <span class="keyword">\infty</span>&#125; P <span class="keyword">\left</span><span class="keyword">\&#123;</span> <span class="keyword">\left</span>| &#123;<span class="keyword">\frac</span> &#123;I<span class="keyword">\left</span>( <span class="keyword">\alpha</span><span class="built_in">_</span>i <span class="keyword">\right</span>)&#125;&#123;N&#125; &#125; - H(s) <span class="keyword">\right</span>| &lt; <span class="keyword">\varepsilon</span> <span class="keyword">\right</span><span class="keyword">\&#125;</span> = 1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\lim _{N\to \infty} P \left{ \left| {\frac {I\left( \alpha_i \right)}{N} } - H(s) \right| &lt; \varepsilon \right} &#x3D; 1<br>$$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x(n) = <span class="keyword">\frac</span> 1 &#123;2<span class="keyword">\pi</span>&#125; <span class="keyword">\int</span> <span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;-<span class="keyword">\pi</span>&#125; <span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\pi</span>&#125; X <span class="keyword">\left</span>( <span class="keyword">\rm</span> e<span class="built_in">^</span>  &#123; &#123;  <span class="keyword">\rm</span> j&#125; <span class="keyword">\omega</span>&#125; <span class="keyword">\right</span>)e<span class="built_in">^</span> &#123; &#123; <span class="keyword">\rm</span> j&#125; <span class="keyword">\omega</span> n&#125; <span class="keyword">\,</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\rm</span> d&#125; <span class="keyword">\omega</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>x(n) &#x3D; \frac 1 {2\pi} \int _{-\pi} ^{\pi} X \left( \rm e^{ {\rm j} \omega} \right)e^{ {\rm j} \omega n} , {\rm d} \omega<br>$$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;align&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\vec</span> B <span class="keyword">\left</span>( <span class="keyword">\vec</span> r <span class="keyword">\right</span>) <span class="built_in">&amp;</span>= </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\frac</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\mu</span><span class="built_in">_</span>0&#125; &#123;4<span class="keyword">\pi</span>&#125; <span class="keyword">\oint</span> <span class="built_in">_</span>C <span class="keyword">\frac</span> &#123;I <span class="keyword">\,</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\rm</span> d&#125; <span class="keyword">\vec</span> l <span class="keyword">\times</span> <span class="keyword">\vec</span> R&#125; &#123;R<span class="built_in">^</span>3&#125; <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">&amp;</span>= <span class="keyword">\frac</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\mu</span><span class="built_in">_</span>0&#125; &#123;4<span class="keyword">\pi</span>&#125; <span class="keyword">\int</span> <span class="built_in">_</span>V <span class="keyword">\frac</span> &#123; &#123;<span class="keyword">\vec</span> J&#125;<span class="built_in">_</span>V <span class="keyword">\times</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\vec</span> R&#125; &#125; &#123;R<span class="built_in">^</span>3&#125; <span class="keyword">\,</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\rm</span> d&#125; V&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;align&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\begin{align}<br>\vec B \left( \vec r \right) &amp;&#x3D;<br>\frac {\mu_0} {4\pi} \oint _C \frac {I , {\rm d} \vec l \times \vec R} {R^3} \<br>&amp;&#x3D; \frac {\mu_0} {4\pi} \int _V \frac { {\vec J}_V \times {\vec R} } {R^3} , {\rm d} V&#39;<br>\end{align}<br>$$</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
